videos.headline: Shi Smith makes incredible one-handed TD grab for South Carolina TD
videos.description: Shi Smith grabs Collin Hill's 11-yard pass with one hand in the end zone to give South Carolina an early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Shi Smith makes incredible one-handed TD grab for South Carolina TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Corral keeps it for a TD to capitalize on Finley's INT
videos.description: A.J. Finley picks off Collin Hill's pass to set up Matt Corral's three-yard touchdown run to give Ole Miss a 14-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Corral keeps it for a TD to capitalize on Finley's INT) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris finds gap for 46-yard TD run
videos.description: Good South Carolina blocking opens up a hole for Kevin Harris who takes it 46 yards to the house to tie the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris finds gap for 46-yard TD run) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris takes it 44 yards for 4th TD of the night
videos.description: Kevin Harris gets loose for a 44-yard touchdown run to put South Carolina ahead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris takes it 44 yards for 4th TD of the night) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kiffin travels down sideline, throws clipboard to celebrate 91-yard Ole Miss TD
videos.description: Matt Corral finds a wide-open Elijah Moore, who takes it the rest of the way for a 91-yard score for Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kiffin travels down sideline, throws clipboard to celebrate 91-yard Ole Miss TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET
